[I] Wayland clipboard utilities

[T] This project implements two command-line Wayland clipboard utilities,
[T] `wl-copy` and `wl-paste`, that let you easily copy data between the clipboard
[T] and Unix pipes, sockets, files and so on.

[U] https://github.com/bugaevc/wl-clipboard

